13
00:00:37,399 --> 00:00:44,760
The World Health Organization, or WHO, recommends a daily salt intake of less than 5 grams,

14
00:00:44,760 --> 00:00:47,000
about the same as a teaspoon.

15
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:51,719
In fact, the human body needs salt, at least 1 gram a day to survive.

16
00:00:51,719 --> 00:00:58,240
But most of us eat far too much, increasing the risk of high blood pressure and heart disease.

17
00:00:58,240 --> 00:01:02,920
In this programme, we'll be asking, how much salt is too much?

