47
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:16,480
This causes high blood pressure, which over time can lead to heart disease.

48
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:20,800
Globally, governments are fighting this health risk in different ways.

49
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:26,120
The Australian government reduced its recommended salt intake to 6 grams a day, while the British

50
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:31,480
government has passed laws forcing food companies to reduce the amount of salt they use, and

51
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:34,920
